name: Frannie Clutch in Leopard Calfhair/ Deerskin
description:
MADE IN NEW ORLEANS

The Frannie clutch has two zippers-one on top and one on the side seam- and each has it's own compartment. In the top zipper, there is a pocket to hold cell phone, change, or whatever your little heart desires.

All bags have a custom designed Kona cotton lining. The zippers are 6MM Riri Zippers with black tape and silver nickel metal.

Grande fits ipad or kindle, cell phone, small to medium wallet, pen, small to large notebook, and keys. (possibly more depending on how hard you try!) Medium and small can fit all of the above with the exception of an iPad!

Cheers!

name: Billie Croc Clutch
description:
MADE IN NEW ORLEANS.

Pictured above in Electric Blue.
The Billie Croc clutch is made from real Caiman crocodile and deerskin. The flap is from the original tail of the croc. There are two compartments- one on top with the flap as closure and a zippered compartment on the right side seam. In the top compartment, there is a pocket to hold cell phone, change, or whatever your little heart desires.

All bags have a custom designed Kona cotton lining. The zippers are 6MM Riri Zippers with black tape and silver nickel metal.

Size varies based on Caimen crocodile size. Estimate size 10x12 in.
Fits cell phone, small wallet, pen, small notebook, and keys. (probably more depending on how hard you try!)
Note: This item is custom and made-to-order. Please expect a 6-8 week delivery date.

Cheers!
